{"tid":995923,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【《老友記》經典角色】麥尼賓被小粉絲誤認為「Joey」爸爸","createTime":"2019-01-25T23:37:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T01:57:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fe22caca90abc34a1b813161371f7cc483871d82","tid":995923,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-25T23:37:55.000Z","msg":"經典美國喜劇《老友記》（Friends）至今已播畢15年，但想不到影響力依然強大。最近主角之一，飾演「Joey」的男星麥尼賓（Matt LeBlanc）就於清談節目上分享到自己被一名13、14歲少年認出，但卻誤認他為Joey爸爸！<br />\n51歲的麥尼賓最近於清談節目《Live with Kelly and Ryan》接受兩位主持訪問，主持Ryan首先指因為串流電視台Netflix買下了《老友記》，所以新一代觀眾都可以看到劇集，之後麥尼賓就分享到自己的經歷：「有一日我在街上行，那已經是幾年前了，有一個孩子，大約13、14歲左右，他突然說：『我的天，你是Joey的爸爸！』之後我的反應是：『走開！』，哈哈，老人家都是這樣嘛。」確實麥尼賓是年老了不少，又滿頭白髮，難怪小粉絲會認錯。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190125/large/1548409489_98fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190125%2Flarge%2F1548409489_98fa.jpg&h=3e37c4df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190125/large/1548409489_0bfd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190125%2Flarge%2F1548409489_0bfd.jpg&h=a3ace2bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0b35286a27cdf9cdb77ebd5e415eed8c6d7befa","tid":995923,"uid":126044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T01:31:25.000Z","msg":"matt leblanc俾人感覺好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 滄桑"},{"pid":"cce158a2bbf504983a7fd464e108fab487de259d","tid":995923,"uid":59669,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T01:35:32.000Z","msg":"how you doin'<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9450c8150a779e4020eda2aae51ba47eb4a9902","tid":995923,"uid":58512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T01:36:57.000Z","msg":"細個明珠台成日睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 